                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18091206-36-off215 t18091206-36-cd216"></join>, a hat, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18091206-36-victim357" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Spibey
               <interp inst="t18091206-36-victim357" type="surname" value="Spibey"></interp>
