                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18091206-36-off215 t18091206-36-victim357"></join>
                  </persName>
            .</p>
               <p>JOHN SPIBEY. I am a <rs id="t18091206-36-viclabel217" type="occupation">hat maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18091206-36-victim357 t18091206-36-viclabel217"></join>, I live at <placeName id="t18091206-36-crimeloc218">No. 9, Broad-street, Bloomsbury</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18091206-36-crimeloc218" type="placeName" value="No. 9, Broad-street, Bloomsbury"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18091206-36-crimeloc218" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18091206-36-off215 t18091206-36-crimeloc218"></join>. On the 7th of September, between four and five in the afternoon, I saw my apprentice collar the prisoner, and a hat which was my property was laying on the ground.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18091206-36-person358">
                  WILLIAM 
                  CONDER
               <interp inst="t18091206-36-person358" type="surname" value="CONDER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18091206-36-person358" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18091206-36-person358" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am apprentice to Mr. Spibey. On the 7th of November I saw the prisoner pass my master's shop three times, he reached his hand in and took a hat that was hanging at the door; I pursued him and took him; he let the hat fall as soon as I took him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. It is the first depreciation that ever I did. The prosecutor has had a good character of me in the neighbourhood that I was brought up from my infancy.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called one witness, who gave him a good character.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18091206-36-verdict219" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18091206-36-verdict219" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, aged 21.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18091206-36-punish220" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18091206-36-punish220" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
